%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hizbul%20Mujahideen%20Terrorist%20Killed%20By%20Security%20Forces%20In%20Kashmir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Hizbul%20Mujahideen%20terrorist%20was%20killed%20as%20security%20forces%20foiled%20an%20infiltration%20attempt%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Poonch%20during%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Monday%2C%20a%20Defence%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20terrorist%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Muneer%20Hussain%2C%20resident%20of%20Bagyladra%20Poonch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20self-styled%20Division%20Commander%20of%20Hizbul%20Mujahideen%2C%20Hussain%20crossed%20LOC%20to%20Pakistan%20Occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%20in%201993%20for%20arms%20training%20and%20returned%20in%201996%20and%20again%20went%20back%20to%20PoK%20in%201998%2C%20said%20the%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20spokesman%20added%20that%20Hussain%20had%20masterminded%20a%20number%20of%20attacks%20on%20security%20forces%20and%20was%20close%20to%20a%20close%20associate%20of%20Maulana%20Dawood%20Kashmir%2C%20who%20in%20turn%20is%20a%20close%20associate%20of%20Syed%20Salauddin%2C%20the%20Hizbul%20Mujahideen%20founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''As%20per%20reliable%20intelligence%20inputs%2C%20a%20high%20level%20meeting%20of%20Hizbul%20Mujahideen%20Group%20took%20place%20in%20Islamabad%20which%20he%20attended.%20Agenda%20of%20the%20meeting%20was%20revival%20of%20terrorism%20in%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%20areas%2C''%20said%20Lt%20Col%20Suneel%20Bartwal%2C%20defense%20spokesman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''It%20is%20evident%20that%20Pak%20is%20trying%20to%20send%20old%20terror%20veterans%20to%20UT%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20to%20motivate%20and%20recruit%20youth%20thus%20making%20desperate%20attempts%20to%20revive%20terrorism%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Army%20said%20an%20infiltration%20attempt%20was%20foiled%20in%20Poonch%20sector%20today%20and%20two%20infiltrators%20were%20shot%20during%20the%20counter-infil