%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20debate%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20his%20government%2C%20PM%20Modi%20used%20'Bharat'%20to%20describe%20the%20country%20and%20attacked%20'INDIA'%20bloc%20by%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20grave%20threat%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20National%20Handloom%20Day%20celebration%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam%2C%20Pragati%20Maidan%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20said%20it%20is%20his%20government's%20endeavour%20to%20make%20India's%20handloom%2C%20Khadi%20and%20the%20textile%20sector%20a%20world%20champion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20highlighted%20various%20steps%20taken%20by%20his%20government%20since%202014%20for%20weavers%20and%20the%20handloom%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20'Vocal%20for%20Local'%20has%20become%20a%20mass%20movement%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20called%20upon%20the%20textile%20sector%20and%20fashion%20industry%20to%20expand%20their%20scope%20and%20work%20to%20make%20India%20a%20USD%205%20trillion%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20the%20country%20is%20witnessing%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20neo-middle%20class%2C%20which%20has%20created%20opportunities%20for%20the%20textile%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20a%20new%20revolution%20has%20come%20in%20the%20country%20regarding%20Swadeshi%20and%20urged%20people%20to%20take%20it%20further%20during%20the%20forthcoming%20festivals%2C%20including%20Raksha%20Bandhan%2C%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%2C%20Dushera%20and%20Diwali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20relevance%20of%20August%209%2C%20he%20said%20the%20date%20has%20been%20a%20witness%20to%20the%20biggest%20movement%20of%20India%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20who%20sent%20the%20message%20of%20Quit%20India%20to%20the%20British.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20said%20the%20same%20mantra%20can%20be%20used%20now%20to%20chase%20away%20such%20elements%20that%20have%20become%20an%20obstacle%20as%20the%20nation%20resolves%20to%20build%20a%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat'%20or%20developed%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20dream%20and%20commitment%20to%20make%20India%20a%20developed%20nation%2C%20but%20there%20are%20evils%20which%20have%20become%20obstacles...Entire%20India%20is%20echoing%20in%20one%20voice%20-%20corruption%2C%20dynasty%2C%20appeasement%20must%20Quit%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underlined%20that%20these%20evils%20in%20India%20are%20a%20big%20challenge%20for%20the%20country%20and%20exuded%20confidence%20that%20the%20nation%20will%20defeat%20these%20evils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20will%20be%20victorious%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%20will%20be%20victorious%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20handloom%20industry%20of%20India%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20confluence%20of%20old%20and%20new%20defines%20the%20new%20India%20of%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20India%20of%20today%20is%20not%20just%20'Local%20for%20Vocal'%20but%20also%20providing%20a%20global%20platform%20to%20take%20it%20to%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20turnover%20of%20Khadi%20and%20village%20industries%20was%20only%20around%20Rs%2025%2C000-30%2C000%20crore%20nine%20years%20ago%20but%20today%20it%20has%20reached%20more%20than%20Rs%201.30%20lakh%20crore.%20The%20additional%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%20has%20reached%20those%20associated%20with%20the%20handloom%20sector%20in%20villages%20and%20the%20tribals%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20reiterated%20the%20need%20to%20repeat%20the%20Swadeshi%20resolution%20to%20support%20weavers%20and%20handicraftsmen%20in%20the%20upcoming%20festivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20'Ekta%20Mall'%20is%20being%20developed%20in%20every%20capital%20city%20of%20states%20by%20the%20government%20to%20promote%20handicraft%20and%20products.%20An%20Ekta%20Mall%20has%20already%20been%20set%20up%20at%20the%20Statue%20of%20Unity%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20neo-middle%20class%20in%20India%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20a%20huge%20young%20consumer%20class%20is%20being%20formed%20for%20every%20product%20and%20it%20presents%20a%20huge%20opportunity%20for%20textile%20companies%2C%20and%20said%20it%20is%20also%20the%20responsibility%20of%20these%20companies%20to%20strengthen%20the%20local%20supply%20chain%20and%20invest%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20want%20to%20take%20advantage%20in%20the%20future%2C%20then%20we%20have%20to%20invest%20in%20local%20supply%20chain%20today.%20This%20is%20the%20way%20to%20build%20a%20developed%20India%20and%20realize%20the%20dream%20of%20a%20USD%205%20trillion%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20the%20textile%20industry%20and%20the%20fashion%20world%20to%20increase%20the%20scope%20of%20thinking%20and%20work%20to%20make%20India%20one%20of%20the%20top%20thee%20economies%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691407080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fek53d3ic_pm-modi_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-opposition-criticism-pm-modis-quit-india-jab-over-dynasty-politics-4276259%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Monday%20said%20certain%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20roadblocks%20in%20making%20India%20a%20developed%20country%2C%20and%20citizens%20are%20now%20demanding%20ills%2C%20like%20corruption%20and%20appeasement%20to%20'Quit%20India'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F