0%26quot%3Bkamikaze%20drone%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20are%20a%20cross%20between%20a%20drone%20and%20a%20guided%20artillery%20shell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELight%20enough%20to%20be%20carried%20by%20foot%20soldiers%20and%20equipped%20with%20a%20warhead%20and%20a%20camera%2C%20they%20can%20orbit%20an%20area%20while%20relaying%20imagery%20to%20an%20operator%20who%20decides%20when%20to%20crash%20it%20into%20a%20target.%20They%20were%20designed%20to%20give%20infantry%20an%20indirect-fire%20capability%20to%20hit%20targets%20shielded%20from%20sight%20by%20terrain%20or%20other%20obstacles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20loitering%20munitions%20such%20as%20the%20US-made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-sends-ukraine-loitering-drones-for-kamikaze-attacks-on-russia-2022-3%5C%22%3ESwitchblade%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20around%20for%20years%2C%20they%20have%20seen%20their%20most%20prolific%20use%20in%20Ukraine.%20Ukrainian%20troops%20have%20often%20strapped%20small%20explosive%20charges%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2023-04-01%2Ffpv-racing-drone-kamikaze-attacks-ukraine-russia-war%2F102155702%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercially%20produced%20quad-copters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turning%20them%20into%20suicide%20drones%20capable%20of%20knocking%20out%20armored%20vehicles%20and%20artillery%20pieces.%20Russia%20has%20used%20military-grade%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rferl.org%2Fa%2Flancet-drones-russia-invasion-counteroffensive-kamikaze%2F32493513.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELancet%203%3C%2Fa%3E%20loitering%20munitions%20to%20hunt%20Ukrainian%20artillery%20and%20disrupt%20Ukraine's%20counteroffensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20which%20makes%20LASSO%20interesting%20on%20multiple%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20an%20indication%20that%20the%20US%20Army%20is%20no%20longer%20keen%20on%20the%20Switchblade%2C%20a%20backpack-size%20loitering%20mun