amming%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20economics%20favor%20the%20cheaper%20drone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20also%20interesting%20about%20LASSO%20is%20that%20the%20Army%20is%20emphasizing%20it%20as%20an%20anti-armor%20weapon.%20%26quot%3BThis%20anti-tank%20capability%20is%20a%20key%20contributor%20to%20our%20efforts%20to%20increase%20the%20lethality%20of%20the%20Army%20of%202030's%20IBCT%20and%20maintain%20overmatch%20against%20our%20near-peer%20threats%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Army%20spokesman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20frequent%20videos%20of%20Ukrainian%20drones%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2JbZEK9kwqQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrashing%20into%20Russian%20tanks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20are%20improvised%20weapons.%20The%20Switchblade%20300's%20warhead%20is%20only%20the%20size%20of%20a%2040%20mm%20grenade%2C%20while%20the%20Switchblade%20600%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20kill%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20is%20expensive.%20It's%20not%20clear%20what%20kind%20of%20warhead%20LASSO%20will%20pack%2C%20and%20the%20Army%20didn't%20mention%20cost%20in%20its%20announcement%2C%20but%20if%20combat%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20a%20guide%2C%20LASSO%20will%20target%20the%20thinner%20armor%20on%20top%20of%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20numerous%20top-attack%20anti-tank%20weapons%20%E2%80%94%20the%20US-made%20Javelin%20missile%20and%20laser-guided%20artillery%20shells%20such%20as%20US's%20Excalibur%20and%20Russia's%20Krasnopol%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%20%E2%80%94%20but%20these%20munitions%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20each.%20If%20the%20Army%20can%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20build%20a%20LASSO%20that's%20powerful%20enough%20to%20destroy%20a%20tank%20but%20cheap%20enough%20for%20mass%20employment%2C%20the%20impact%20could%20be%20immense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20P