cted%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20he%20said%2C%20demolishes%20the%20triple%20chain%20of%20accountability.%20It%20means%20the%20officers%20will%20not%20listen%20to%20the%20Chief%20minister%20or%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20go%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%2025%20years%2C%20BJP%20lost%20six%20state%20elections%2C%20even%20in%202015%20and%202020.%20They%20know%20they%20can't%20any%20win%20elections%20in%2025%20next%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chadha%20said%2C%20repeating%20his%20party's%20argument%20that%20this%20is%20BJP%20backlash%20to%20AAP's%20sweeping%20victory%20in%20two%20consecutive%20elections.%20The%20party%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20BJP%20to%20trying%20to%20control%20Delhi%20through%20its%20representative%2C%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20stance%20towards%20Delhi%2C%20he%20added%2C%20flies%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20cherished%20views%20of%20its%20tallest%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20LK%20Advani.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVajpayee%20and%20deputy%20PM%20Advani%20brought%20a%20bill%20to%20give%20Delhi%20the%20status%20of%20state.%20The%20BJP%20National%20Executive%20decided%20to%20give%20statehood%20to%20Delhi.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20promising%20people%20that%20they%20would%20make%20Delhi%20a%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chadha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20Amit%20Shah%20ji%2C%20don't%20be%20Nehruvadi%2C%20be%20Advaniwadi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20also%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20insulting%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20crisis%20came%20that%20you%20had%20to%20go%20against%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%3F%20This%20is%20an%20insult%20of%20the%20country's%20top%20court.%20The%20BJP%20given%20a%20message%20that%20it%20doesn't%20care%20what%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20says%2C%20they%20have%20challenged%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20executive%20order%20that%20was%20passed%20barely%20a%20week%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20AAP%20government.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ordinance%20and%20the%20proposed%20law%20to%20replace%20it%20over-rides%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20that%20ceded%20Delhi's%20administrative%20control%20to%20the%20elected%20government.%20After%20an%20eight-year%20tussle%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20ruled%20that%20the%20elected%20government%20is%20the%20boss%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ordinance%20created%20a%20National%20Capital%20Civil%20Services%20Authority%20which%20is%20tasked%20with%20postings%20and%20transfers%20of%20bureaucrats%20serving%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20the%20Principal%20Home%20Secretary%20are%20members%20who%20can%20vote%20on%20issues.%20The%20final%20arbiter%20is%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691406240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fqjbgnmek_raghav-chadha_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraghav-chadha-on-delhi-bill-because-bjp-couldnt-win-delhi-for-25-years-4276328%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20Raghav%20Chadha%20launched%20a%20blistering%20attack%20on%20the%20government%20today%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20bill%20in%20parliament%2C%20exhorting%20the%20BJP%20to%20follow%20their%20own%20leaders%20--%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20LK%20Advani.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraghav-chadha-on-delhi-bill-because-bjp-couldnt-win-delhi-for-25-years-4276328%22%2C%22cdnA