%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20strife-torn%20Manipur.%20The%20ambit%20of%20the%20committee%20will%20be%20wider%20than%20just%20probing%20incidents%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20efforts%20are%20to%20restore%20a%20sense%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20We%20will%20constitute%20at%20one%20level%20a%20committee%20of%20three%20former%20HC%20judges.%20This%20committee%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20things%20apart%20from%20investigation%20-%20including%20relief%2C%20remedial%20measures%20etc.%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20will%20be%20Justice%20Gita%20Mittal%20(former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20HC)%2C%20Justice%20Shalini%20Joshi%20(former%20Judge%20of%20Bombay%20High%20Court)%2C%20and%20Justice%20Asha%20Menon%20(former%20judge%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Court)%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20IPS%20officer%20Dattatray%20Padsalgikar%20will%20oversee%20the%20CBI%20investigation%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20will%20be%20five%20officers%20of%20at%20least%20the%20rank%20of%20DySP%2C%20brought%20into%20the%20CBI%20from%20various%20states.%20These%20officers%20will%20also%20be%20functioning%20within%20the%20four%20corners%20of%20infrastructure%20and%20administrative%20structure%20of%20CBI%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%2042%20SITs%20looking%20at%20cases%20which%20have%20not%20been%20transferred%20to%20CBI.%20These%20SITs%20should%20be%20supervised%20by%20DIG%20ranked%20officers%20from%20outside%20Manipur.%20Each%20officer%20will%20monitor%20six%20SITs%20to%20see%20that%20the%20investigation%20is%20going%20correctly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict-wise%20Special%20Investigation%20Teams%20will%20be%20formed%20to%20probe%20cases%20related%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-violence-latest-updates-imphal-news-live-manipur-news-6-dead-in-24-hours-in-fresh-manipur-violence-deadliest-day-in-a-fortnight-4273328%5C%22%3Eviolence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Centre%20today%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20reserved%20its%20order%20on%20the%20plea%20seeking%20Court%20Monitored%20Committee%20to%20investigate%20violence%20related%20cases%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Rajiv%20Singh%20was%20present%20in%20the%20hearing%20before%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20to%20answer%20queries%20on%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20and%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20administration%20so%20far%2C%20besides%20the%20segregation%20of%20cases%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20effective%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20allowing%20any%20external%20investigation%2C%20let%20SITs%20be%20formed%20at%20district%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Attorney%20General%20R%20Venkataramani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20are%20more%20than%2011%20First%20Information%20Reports%2C%20or%20FIRs%2C%20pertaining%20to%20crime%20against%20women%20which%20are%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20they%20will%20be%20probed%20by%20district%20level%20SITs%20headed%20by%20a%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20rank%20officer%2C%20who%20will%20all%20be%20women%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CBI%20team%2C%20which%20will%20be%20investigating%20this%2C%20has%20two%20lady%20SP%20officers.%20CBI%20has%20officers%20from%20all%20across%20the%20country.%20We%20have%20taken%20that%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Attorney%20General%20told%20the%20court%20the%20government%20is%20handling%20the%20situation%20on%20a%20very%20mature%20level%2C%20and%20has%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20with%20segregation%20of%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Indira%20Jaising%20argued%20the%20conflict%20is%20ongoing%2C%20and%20suggested%20a%20two-fold%20approach%20--%20investigation%20and%20prevention%20of%20further%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Nizam%20Pasha%2C%20who%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20last%20month%20lauded%20for%20his%20valuable%20and%20%26quot%3Bfair%26quot%3B%20suggestions%20aimed%20at%20mitigating%20the%20ongoing%20crisis%2C%20said%20there%20are%2016%20FIRs%20which%20are%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20all%20of%20them%20need%20to%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20calling%20it%20an%20SIT%20but%20it%20is%20selected%20by%20state...The%20allegations%20are%20against%20the%20state%20police%20--%20ranging%20from%20active%20participation%20to%20perpetration.%20The%20concern%20of%20selection%20doesn't%20get%20elevated%20if%20the%20selection%20is%20by%20state%20cadre.%20Selection%20should%20be%20by%20court.%C2%A0For%20public%20prosecutors%2C%20it%20should%20be%20law%20officers%20from%20other%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20argued%20there%20has%20to%20be%20an%20independent%20body%20to%20investigate%20supply%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20argued%20it%20may%20not%20be%20appropriate%20to%20not%20trust%20the%20police%20with%20the%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20not%20be%20appropriate%20not%20to%20trust%20the%20police%20officers.%20For%20the%20proposed%20committee%20to%20be%20constituted%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20let%20judicial%20officers%20alone%20be%20included%2C%20not%20the%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20SG%20Mehta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%201%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said%20there%20was%20a%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20law%20and%20order%20and%20constitutional%20machinery%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20had%20rapped%20the%20state%20police%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Btardy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Blethargic%26quot%3B%20probe%20of%20incidents%20of%20ethnic%20violence%2C%20especially%20those%20targeting%20women%2C%20and%20had%20summoned%20the%20DGP%20to%20answer%20its%20queries%20on%20August%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20urged%20the%20bench%20that%20instead%20of%20the%20two%20FIRs%20related%20to%20a%20video%20showing%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20mob%2C%2011%20out%20of%206%2C523%20FIRs%20linked%20to%20violence%20against%20women%20and%20children%20may%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20tried%20out%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20was%20today%20hearing%20around%2010%20petitions%20relating%20to%20the%20violence%20seeking%20reliefs%2C%20including%20court-monitored%20probe%2C%20into%20cases%20besides%20measures%20for%20rehabilitation%20and%20other%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691405460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fkemtllr_manipur_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdistrict-level-teams-will-probe-cases-manipur-government-to-supreme-court-4276146%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manipur%20violence%3A%20District-wise%20Special%20Investigation%20Teams%20will%20be%20formed%20to%20investigate%20the%20cases%20related%20to%20violence%20in%20strife-torn%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Centre%20today%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdistrict-level-teams-will-probe-cases-manipur-government-to-supreme-court-4276146%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdistrict-level-teams-will-probe-cases-manipur-government-to-supreme-court-4276146%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdistrict-level-teams-will-probe-cases-manipur-government-to-supreme-court-4276146%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%206%20deal%3A%20Save%20an%20extra%20%2450%20instantly%20at%20checkout%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20wid