go.%20The%20bag%20did%20not%20arrive%20and%20Ms%20Shuster%20called%20the%20toll-free%20number%20for%20lost%20baggage%2C%20the%20media%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%2C%20'Your%20bag's%20going%20to%20come%20in%20later%20today%20on%20one%20of%20two%20flights.'%20I%20said%20'OK%2C%20great%2C'%20but%20it%20never%20came.%20So%20I%20called%20later%20that%20afternoon%20and%20they%20said%20'Your%20bag%20is%20still%20in%20Baltimore%2C'%26quot%3B%20says%20Ms%20Shuster%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%2C%20Ms%20Shuster%20knew%20that%20her%20bag%20was%20not%20in%20Baltimore%20after%20she%20started%20her%20bag%20on%20Apple%20AirTag.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20unique%20equipment%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20check%20it.%20Airlines%20are%20getting%20worse%2C%20rates%20of%20lost%20luggage%20are%20getting%20higher%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20where%20it%20was%20-%20so%20I%20bought%20the%20tag%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AirTag%20showed%20that%20the%20bag%20was%20at%20O'Hare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20them%20I%20could%20see%20it%20at%20Terminal%201%20baggage%20reclaim%20in%20Chicago%2C%20and%20they%20said%20'We%20have%20no%20record%20of%20it.'%20I%20asked%20them%20to%20call%20Chicago%2C%20and%20they%20said%20'No%2C%20we're%20not%20allowed.'%20They%20said%20they'd%20put%20notes%20in%20the%20system%20and%20the%20baggage%20team%20would%20take%20care%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20told%20her%20that%20she%20had%20the%20wrong%20claim%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shuster's%20daughter%20borrowed%20some%20kit%20for%20that%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20airline%20kept%20saying%20that%20the%20bag%20was%20stolen%2C%20Ms%20Shuster%20was%20convinced%20it%20was%20still%20there.%20%26quot%3BIt%20had%20moved%20maybe%2050%20feet%2C%20and%20the%20AirTag%20was%20embedded%20in%20the%20bag%20-%20I%20doubted%20someone%20stole%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20implying%20it%20could%20be%20a%20double%20win%20but%20I%20wasn't%20trying%20to%20game%20the%20system%20-%20to%20replace%20what%20was%20in%20that%20bag%20was%20much%20harder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20reached%20out%20to%20United's%20Twitter%20team%2C%20but%20they%20said%20they%20couldn't%20locate%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20let%20our%20baggage%20team%20in%20ORD%20know%20that%20you'll%20be%20arriving%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20initially%20replied%20-%20before%20half%20an%20hour%20later%20messaging%20again%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20recommend%20that%20you%20remain%20in%20Denver%20while%20we%20continue%20to%20work%20through%20our%20processes%20to%20bring%20your%20bag%20back%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20did%20not%20trust%20United's%20processes.%20So%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20next%20flight%20to%20Chicago%20and%20get%20her%20lost%20luggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20jumped%20on%20the%20plane%2C%20flew%20to%20Chicago%2C%20got%20to%20baggage%20claim%2C%20and%20it%20took%20them%2030%20seconds%20to%20give%20me%20my%20bag%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeanwhile%20I'd%20already%20sent%20pictures%20of%20the%20bag%2C%20the%20claim%20ticket%20and%20its%20location%20to%20United.%20It's%20gobsmacking%20that%20they%20can't%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20do%20it%20better%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691402580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Faf0cs4s8_airtag-650_625x300_02_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-woman-tracks-lost-luggage-via-airtag-flies-to-collect-it-4276302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20the%20pair%20arrived%20at%20Denver%20after%20midnight%2C%20they%20couldn't%20find%20their%20bag%20on%20the%20belt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature