rdik-pandya-reminded-of-unique-comment-after-captaincy-blunder-cost-india-2nd-t20i-4275902%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fhardik-pandya-reminded-of-unique-comment-after-captaincy-blunder-cost-india-2nd-t20i-4275902%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20MP's%20%5C%22First%20They%20Came...%5C%22%20Warning%20For%20Parties%20Backing%20Delhi%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20during%20the%20Delhi%20services%20Bill%20debate%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcontrol-freak%20sarkar%26quot%3B%20and%20warning%20the%20political%20parties%20backing%20the%20centre%20on%20this%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Delhi's%20special%20constitutional%20status%20was%20created%2C%20be%20it%20BJP%20or%20Congress%20or%20any%20other%20color%20of%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20has%20tried%20to%20overrule%20two%20Constitution%20Bench%20judgments%20qua%20the%20status%20of%20NCT%3F%20Why%20did%20no%20government%20create%20an%20authority%2C%20where%20the%20CM%20of%20Delhi%20is%20in%20a%20minority%3F%20Why%20did%20no%20government%20empower%20two%20bureaucrats%20to%20overrule%20an%20elected%20CM%3F%20Why%20did%20no%20government%20make%20the%20LG%2Cwho%20is%20a%20constitutional%20figurehead%20except%20in%20three%20areas%2C%20into%20a%20Super%20CM%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%2C%20a%20renowned%20lawyer%2C%20asked%20rhetorically%20why%20no%20previous%20government%20made%20all%20agencies%20of%20Delhi%20%26quot%3Bsubject%20to%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20for%20appointment%20of%20its%20heads%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20government%2C%20and%20this%20bill%20does%20it%20all!%20Something%20not%20done%20earlier.%20Why%20has%20nobody%20done%20it%20earlier%3F%20Because%20it%20is%20the%20fitrat%20(nature)%20of%20this%20Control%20Freak%20Sarkar%20whose%20visiting%20card%20is%20vendetta%20identity%20badge%20is%20of%20a%20graceless%20and%20fuming%20loser%2C%20whose%20approach%20is%20to%20control%2C%20control%20n%20control%20everything%2C%20by%20hook%20or%20crook%20and%20usually%20more%20by%20crook%20than%20by%20hook%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20quoted%20German%20theologian%20Martin%20Niemoller's%20timeless%20lines%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20they%20came...%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20warn%20political%20parties%20that%20have%20announced%20support%20to%20the%20centre%20on%20the%20Delhi%20services%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20collectively%20oppose%20this%20cause%20one%20day%20this%20federalism%20knock%20could%20come%20at%20your%20door.%20Sabka%20number%20aayega%20(everyone's%20turn%20will%20come)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20then%20quoted%20quoted%20Niemoller%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20they%20came%20for%20the%20socialists%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20speak%20out%20because%20I%20was%20not%20a%20socialist.%20Then%20they%20came%20for%20the%20trade%20unionists%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20speak%20out%20because%20I%20was%20not%20a%20trade%20unionist.%20Then%20they%20came%20for%20the%20Jews%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20speak%20out%20because%20I%20was%20not%20a%20Jew.%20Then%20they%20came%20for%20me%20and%20there%20was%20no%20one%20left%20to%20speak%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lines%2C%20used%20by%20Niemoller%20to%20criticise%20the%20silence%20of%20German%20intellectuals%20and%20religious%20leaders%20during%20the%20rise%20of%20Nazism%2C%20is%20routinely%20used%20to%20hit%20out%20at%20people%20who%20do%20not%20speak%20out%20against%20authoritarian%20regimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691401980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F4r5fiek8_abhishek-singhvi_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-services-bill-