0and%20South%20Africa.%20Four%20cubs%20had%20been%20born%20there%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECheetahs%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20park%20as%20part%20of%20a%20reintroduction%20project%20after%20the%20species%20was%20declared%20extinct%20from%20the%20country%20in%201952.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20year%20since%20the%20cheetahs%20have%20been%20translocated%20(from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%20in%20September%202022%20and%20February%20this%20year%20respectively)%2C%20the%20government%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20continuous%20work%20is%20going%20on%20regarding%20the%20weather%20conditions%20here%20and%20its%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20preparation.%20Every%20year%20there%20will%20be%2012-14%20new%20cheetahs%20brought%20in.%20There%20are%20problems%20but%20nothing%20alarming%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20have%20attributed%20the%20deaths%20to%20sub-standard%20radio%20collars%20used%20on%20the%20cheetahs.%20While%20the%20government%20has%20dismissed%20the%20charges%20as%20%26quot%3Bspeculation%20and%20hearsay%20without%20scientific%20evidence%26quot%3B%2C%20NDTV%20had%20accessed%20footage%20that%20shows%20authorities%20examining%20the%20collar%20and%20a%20maggot-infested%20wound%20on%20the%20neck%20of%20Suraj%2C%20who%20had%20died%20on%20July%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20today%2C%20denied%20any%20lapses%20and%20said%20that%20foreign%20experts%20had%20been%20consulted%20before%20making%20the%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691400360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F57jbfo4_sasha-cheetah_650x400_27_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-reasons-to-doubt-centres-arguments-supreme-court-on-cheetah-deaths-4275941%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20big%20relief%20for%20the%20government%2C%20the%20S