o%20previously%20lead%20the%20core%20search%20algorithms%20group%20at%20Google.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Norvig%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20spent%20several%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20directing%20the%20company's%20core%20search%20algorithms%20group%20and%20later%20moved%20into%20a%20role%20as%20the%20director%20of%20research%20where%20he%20oversaw%20teams%20on%20machine%20translation%2C%20speech%20recognition%2C%20and%20computer%20vision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorvig%20has%20also%20rotated%20through%20several%20academic%20institutions%20over%20the%20years%20as%20a%20former%20faculty%20member%20at%20UC-Berkeley%2C%20former%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%2C%20and%20now%2C%20a%20fellow%20at%20Stanford's%20center%20for%20Human-Centered%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorvig%20told%20Insider%20by%20email%20that%20%26quot%3BAI%20research%20is%20at%20a%20very%20exciting%20moment%2C%20when%20we%20are%20beginning%20to%20see%20models%20that%20can%20perform%20well%20(but%20not%20perfectly)%20on%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20general%20tasks.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20however%2C%20that%20%26quot%3Bjust%20as%20with%20the%20Internet%2C%20there%20is%20a%20danger%20that%20these%20powerful%20AI%20models%20can%20be%20used%20maliciously%20by%20unscrupulous%20people%20to%20spread%20disinformation%20rather%20than%20information.%20An%20important%20area%20of%20current%20research%20is%20to%20defend%20against%20such%20attacks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETimnit%20Gebru%20is%20a%20computer%20scientist%20who%E2%80%99s%20become%20known%20for%20her%20work%20in%20addressing%20bias%20in%20AI%20algorithms.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Timnit%20Gebru%20%E2%80%93%20TechCrunch%20Disrupt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cba4600f3dff0019560e50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption