%3E%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDemis%20Hassabis%20has%20said%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20will%20be%20here%20in%20a%20few%20years.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222415%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DeepMind%20boss%20Demis%20Hassabis%20believes%20AGI%20will%20be%20here%20in%20a%20few%20years.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64522a4c590d7f0018b79d54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221811%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDemis%20Hassabis%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%20of%20machine%20learning%20startup%20DeepMind.%3Cp%3ESamuel%20de%20Roman%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%2C%20a%20former%20child%20chess%20prodigy%20who%20studied%20at%20Cambridge%20and%20University%20College%20London%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-incredible-life-of-deepmind-cofounder-demis-hassabis-2017-5%5C%22%3Enicknamed%20the%20%26quot%3Bsuperhero%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20The%20Guardian%20back%20in%202016.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20handful%20of%20research%20stints%2C%20and%20a%20venture%20in%20videogames%2C%20he%20founded%20DeepMind%20in%202010.%20He%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2014%2Fjan%2F27%2Fgoogle-acquires-uk-artificial-intelligence-startup-deepmind%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esold%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20AI%20lab%20to%20Google%20in%202014%20for%20%C2%A3400%20million%20where%20he's%20worked%20on%20algorithms%20to%20tackle%20issues%20in%20healthcare%2C%20climate%20change%2C%20and%20also%20launched%20a%20research%20unit%20dedicated%20to%20the%20understanding%20the%20ethical%20and%20social%20impact%20of%20AI%20in%202017%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deepmind.com%2Fblog%2Fwhy-we-launch