ited%20about%20the%20people%20she%20works%20with%20across%20the%20world%20%26quot%3Bwho%20are%20committed%20to%20more%20sustainable%2C%20consent-based%2C%20and%20equitable%20approaches%20to%20using%20generative%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20however%2C%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20we%20don't%20approach%20AI%20development%20with%20care%20and%20caution%2C%20and%20without%20the%20right%20regulatory%20safeguards%2C%20it%20could%20produce%20extreme%20concentrations%20of%20power%2C%20with%20dangerously%20anti-democratic%20effects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMargaret%20Mitchell%20is%20the%20chief%20ethics%20scientist%20at%20Hugging%20Face.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221487%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Margaret%20Mitchell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd2a5df5d4870019e1c57c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221115%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMargaret%20Mitchell%20has%20headed%20AI%20projects%20at%20several%20big%20tech%20companies.%3Cp%3EMargaret%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMitchell%20has%20published%20more%20than%20100%20papers%20over%20the%20course%20of%20her%20career%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.m-mitchell.com%2Fbio%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20her%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20spearheaded%20AI%20projects%20across%20various%20big%20tech%20companies%20including%20Microsoft%20and%20Google.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202020%2C%20Mitchell%20published%20a%20paper%20on%20the%20dangers%20of%20large%20language%20models%2C%20along%20with%20Timnit%20Gebru%2C%20who%20was%20then%20the%20co-lead%20of%20Google's%20ethical%20artificial%20intelligence.%20The%20paper%20spurred%20disagreements%20between%20the%20researchers%20and%20Google's%20management%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20Gebru's%20departure%20from%20the%20company%20in%20December%202020.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-fires-ai-ethics-researcher-margaret-mitchell-2021-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DGoogle%2520has%2520fired%2520another%2520AI%2Cof%2520Insider%2520for%2520more%2520stories%5C%22%3EMitchell%20was%20terminated%20by%20Google%20just%20two%20months%20later%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20February%202021%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20at%20Hugging%20Face%20%E2%80%94%20an%20open-source%20data%20science%20and%20machine%20learning%20platform%20that%20was%20founded%20in%202016%20%E2%80%94%20she's%20thinking%20about%20how%20to%20democratize%20access%20to%20the%20tools%20necessary%20to%20building%20and%20deploying%20large-scale%20AI%20models.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Morning%20Brew%2C%20where%20Mitchell%20explained%20what%20it%20means%20to%20design%20responsible%20AI%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emergingtechbrew.com%2Fstories%2F2021%2F10%2F04%2Fai-ethics-pioneer-margaret-mitchell-on-her-five-year-plan-at-open-source-ai-startup-hugging-face%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20started%20on%20my%20path%20toward%20working%20on%20what's%20now%20called%20AI%20in%202004%2C%20specifically%20with%20an%20interest%20in%20aligning%20AI%20closer%20to%20human%20behavior.%20Over%20time%2C%20that's%20evolved%20to%20become%20less%20about%20mimicking%20humans%20and%20more%20about%20accounting%20for%20human%20behavior%20and%20working%20with%20humans%20in%20assistive%20and%20augmentative%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENavrina%20Singh%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Credo%20AI%2C%20an%20AI%20governance%20platform.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Navrina%20Singh%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd2dd1f5d4870019e1cac6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22510%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENavrina%20Singh%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Credo%20AI%2C%20says%20the%20system%20may%20help%20people%20reach%20their%20potential.%3Cp%3ENavrina%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECredo%20AI%20is%20essentially%20a%20platform%20that%20helps%20companies%20make%20sure%20they're%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20growing%20body%20of%20regulations%20around%20AI%20usage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider%2C%20Singh%20said%20that%20by%20automating%20the%20systems%20that%20shape%20our%20lives%2C%20AI%20has%20the%20capacity%20%26quot%3Bfree%C2%A0us%20to%20realize%20our%20potential%20in%20every%20area%20where%20it's%20implemented.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20she%20contends%20that%20algorithms%20right%20now%20lack%20the%20human%20judgement%20that's%20necessary%20to%20adapt%20to%20a%20changing%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20integrate%20AI%20into%20civilization's%20fundamental%20infrastructure%2C%20these%20tradeoffs%20take%20on%20existential%20implications%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20forge%20ahead%2C%20the%20responsibility%20to%20harmonize%20human%20values%20and%20ingenuity%20with%20algorithmic%20precision%20is%20non-negotiable.%20Responsible%20AI%20governance%20is%20paramount.%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-godfather-top-names-possibilities-dangers-openai-chatgpt-list-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691398920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd66e220f1cf0019cb2526%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-godfather-top-names-possibilities-dangers-openai-chatgpt-list-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20is%20storming%20its%20way%20to%20front%20page%20of%20society.%20But%20how%20did%20we%20get%20here%3F%20Insider%20takes%20a%20look%20at%20leaders%20in%20the%20f