3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cbf9b10f3dff0019569d0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGU%20sells%20basics%20as%20well%20as%20trendy%20pieces%20for%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennials.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGU%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20Japanese%20retailer%20Fast%20Retailing%20Group%2C%20has%20grown%20to%20nearly%20450%20stores%20in%20Asia%20but%20didn't%20enter%20the%20US%20market%20until%20it%20opened%20its%20Soho%20store%20in%20October%202022.%20From%20September%202021%20to%20August%202022%2C%20GU's%20sales%20totaled%20%241.7%20billion%20which%20made%20up%20about%2011%25%20of%20Fast%20Retailing's%20revenue%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.modernretail.co%2Foperations%2Fwhy-uniqlos-sister-company-gu-is-expanding-into-the-u-s%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERetail%20Dive%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGU's%20name%20is%20pronounced%20as%20just%20the%20letters%2C%20meant%20to%20sound%20like%20the%20Japanese%20word%20%26quot%3Bjiyu%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20freedom.%20Much%20like%20Uniqlo%2C%20GU%20carries%20basics%20like%20logo-free%20t-shirts%2C%20simple%20sweaters%2C%20minimalist%20shoes%2C%20and%20dressy-casual%20pants.%20However%2C%20GU's%20prices%20are%20slightly%20cheaper%20than%20Uniqlo's.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20men's%20open-collar%20shirt%20costs%20%2419.90%20at%20GU%2C%20while%20a%20similar%20style%20goes%20for%20%2439.90%20at%20Uniqlo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22several%20shelves%20of%20folded%20pants%2C%20cargo%20pants%20hang%20from%20rales%2C%20and%20two%20polo%20shirts%20hang%20from%20the%20wall%20inside%20a%20GU%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cbfa790b651c00193a325e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGU%20stocks%20basics%20like%20button-down%20shirts%2C%20polos%2C%20and%20cargo%20pants.%20%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGU%20is%20where%20Chris%20Why%2C%2034%2C%20gets%20his%20basics%2C%20like%20the%20tank%20top%20he%20picked%20up%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20needed%20something%20inexpensive%20but%20nice%20quality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20likes%20to%20wear%20designer%20clothes%2C%20but%20prefers%20to%20save%20money%20on%20simple%20shirts%20he%20can%20pair%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20go%20to%20Forever%2021%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20he%20pointed%20to%20the%20store%20across%20the%20street.%20%26quot%3BYou%20might%20get%20a%20nice%20shirt%2C%20but%20it%20will%20say%20'Undefeated'%20on%20the%20back.%20Here%2C%20it's%20just%20plain%20simple%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20trait%20that%20sets%20GU%20apart%20is%20that%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20more%20sensitive%20to%20fashion%20trends%20than%20its%20sister%20brand.%20While%20Uniqlo's%20range%20of%20styles%20remains%20fairly%20consistent%20from%20season%20to%20season%2C%20GU%20switches%20up%20its%20offerings%20to%20capitalize%20on%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emajor%20fashion%20trends%20and%20pop%20culture%20moments%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20younger%20shopper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22tiktok%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20cite%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40laytonlamell%2Fvideo%2F7246582049044319534%5C%22%20data-video-id%3D%5C%227246582049044319534%5C%22%20data-embed-from%3D%5C%22oembed%5C%22%3E%20%3Csection%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40laytonlamell%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%40laytonlamell%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40laytonlamell%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20fit%20from%20earlier%2C%20all%20love%20to