20and%20learned%20how%20infuriating%20%E2%80%94%20or%20easy%20%E2%80%94%20long-haul%20electric%20travel%20can%20be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECharging%20can%20take%20a%20frustratingly%20long%20time%20in%20the%20wrong%20car%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%202023%20Toyota%20bZ4X%20AWD%20Limited%20electric%20SUV%20sits%20in%20the%20shade%2C%20parked%20by%20a%20charging%20stall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642c37c8fcb86b0018031131%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202023%20Toyota%20bZ4X%20AWD%20Limited%20charging.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20lowdown%20on%20the%20two%20trips%20I%20took%20from%20New%20York%20City.%20The%20first%2C%20behind%20the%20wheel%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoyota-bz4x-electric-car-road-trip-charging-time-range-2023-4%5C%22%3EToyota's%20new%20BZ4X%20SUV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20took%20me%20to%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20For%20the%20second%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Cape%20Cod%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhyundai-ev-genesis-gv60-suv-crystal-sphere-tesla-rival-2023-8%5C%22%3EGenesis%20GV60%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20small%20SUV%20from%20Hyundai's%20luxury%20offshoot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoincidentally%2C%20both%20round%20trips%20totaled%20around%20500%20miles%2C%20required%20two%20charging%20stops%20(one%20on%20each%20leg%20of%20the%20journey)%2C%20plus%20an%20additional%20top-up%20at%20each%20destination.%20But%20one%20experience%20was%20vastly%20more%20enjoyable%2C%20and%20that%20mostly%20comes%20down%20to%20how%20fast%20%E2%80%94%20or%20excruciatingly%20slow%20in%20the%20Toyota's%20case%20%E2%80%94%20each%20SUV%20was%20able%20to%20charge%20up%20and%20get%20me%20back%20on%20the%20road.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20DC%20trip%2C%20I%20stopped%20for%20a%20whopping%20two%20hours%20to%20charge%2C%20turning%20nine%20hours%20of%20travel%20time%20into%2011.%20On%20the%20way%20to%20and%20from%20Cape%20Cod%2C%20I%20stopped%20for%20a%20much%20more%20manageable%2047%20minutes.%20That's%20longer%20than%20a%20couple%20of%20gas%20stops%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20convenient%20enough.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20Genesis%20GV60%20electric%20SUV%20charging%20at%20an%20EVgo%20station%2C%20with%20trees%20and%20sky%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd3d098df5080019d32bec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Genesis%20GV60%20charging.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20the%20big%20gap%3F%20Every%20EV%20comes%20with%20a%20maximum%20rate%2C%20expressed%20in%20kilowatts%20(kW)%2C%20at%20which%20it%20can%20accept%20power%20from%20roadside%20charging%20stations.%20The%20higher%20a%20model's%20rating%2C%20the%20quicker%20it%20can%20theoretically%20recharge%20its%20battery%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20you%20find%20a%20plug%20with%20a%20kW%20rating%20that's%20equal%20to%20or%20greater%20than%20your%20car's.%20(I%20say%20%26quot%3Btheoretically%26quot%3B%20because%20lots%20of%20factors%2C%20from%20the%20outside%20temperature%20to%20the%20state%20of%20the%20charging%20station%20itself%2C%20could%20affect%20the%20actual%20duration%20of%20your%20session.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoyota-bz4x-suv-review-tesla-rival-range-charging-problem-photos-2023-4%5C%22%3EBZ4X%20Limited%20AWD%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Toyota%20lent%20me%20rates%20at%20an%20unimpressive%20100%20kW.%20The%20higher-tech%20GV60%20maxes%20out%20at%20around%20230%20kW%20in%20my%20experience.%20The%20even%20bigger%20snag%20was%20that%20I%20never%20observed%20close%20to%20the%20Toyota's%20top%20rate%2C%20leading%20to%20some%20long%20and%20boring%20charging%20sessions.%20A%20Toyota%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20BZ4X%20sometimes%20slows%20down%20fast-charging%20to%20reduce%20wear%20on%20the%20battery%20pack%20and%20increase%20its%20lifespan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%202023%20Toyota%20bZ4X%20AWD%20Limited%2C%20viewed%20from%20the%20front%20against%20a%20blue%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642c37c4fcb86b0018031126%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202023%20Toyota%20bZ4X%20AWD%20Limited%20charging.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20first%20stop%20in%20the%20Toyota%2C%20it%20refused%20to%20pull%20more%20than%2035%20kW%2C%20so%2037%25%20to%2074%25%20%E2%80%94%20or%2095%20miles%20of%20estimated%20range%20%E2%80%94%20took%20a%20full%2045%20minutes.%20In%20DC%2C%203%25%20to%2077%25%20took%20an%20hour.%20On%20the%20ride%20home%2C%20the%20BZ4X%20maxed%20out%20at%2050%20kW%2C%20so%20charging%20from%206%25%20to%2080%25%20ate%20up%20an%20hour%20and%2015%20minutes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContrast%20that%20with%20my%20breezy%20Genesis%20experience.%20First%20stop%3A%20a%20quick%2C%2012-minute%20top-up%20from%2049%25%20to%2080%25.%20Second%20stop%3A%2015%25%20to%2094%25%20in%2035%20minutes.%20Both%20times%20I%20plugged%20in%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-genesis-gv60-electric-suv-tesla-rival-review-2023-7%5C%22%3Ethe%20GV60%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20sucking%20in%20electricity%20at%20over%20230%20kW%20almost%20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20charging%20cable%20is%20shown%20plugged%20into%20the%202023%20Toyota%20bZ4X%20AWD%20Limited%20electric%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642c37d8fcb86b0018031162%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202023%20Toyota%20bZ4X%20AWD%20Limited%20charging.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20convinced%20me%20that%20charging%20speed%20is%20way%20more%20important%20than%20a%20vehicle's%20total%20range.%20Although%20the%20EPA%20says%20these%20two%20vehicles%20can%20travel%20similar%20distances%20on%20a%20full%20charge%20(222%20miles%20for%20the%20Toyota%20and%20235%20miles%20for%20the%20Genesis)%2C%20one%20is%20clearly%20better%20suited%20for%20long%20trips.%20But%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20100-kW%20charging%20plugs%20are%20more%20common%20than%20ones%20that%20can%20provide%20200%20kW%20and%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20remember%20that%20the%20vast%20and%20mostly%20exclusive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-only-ev-worth-buying-right-now-charging-nacs-ccs-2023-7%5C%22%3ETesla%20Supercharger%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20means%20extended%20drives%20are%20simpler%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-owners-share-unexpected-headaches-owning-ev-electric-car-2023-7%5C%22%3ETesla%20owners%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20buyers%20of%20other%20EVs.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20drivers%20can%20input%20a%20destination%20into%20their%20car's%20navigation%20system%2C%20and%20the%20vehicle%20will%20suggest%20a%20route%20that%20includes%20pit%20stops.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20love%20or%20hate%20your%20Tesla%20or%20other%20EV%3F%20Never%20buying%20an%20electric%20car%20in%20a%20million%20years%3F%20I%20want%20to%20hear%20your%20thoughts%20about%20EVs.%20Contact%20me%20at%20tlevin%40insider.com%20and%20share%20your%20story!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECold%20weather%20can%20put%20the%20chill%20on%20a%20road%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20differentiating%20factor%20between%20these%20two%20journeys%20%E2%80%94%20aside%20from%20the%20vehicle%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20was%20the%20time%20of%20year.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-car-polestar-2-cold-weather-driving-range-2022-1%5C%22%3ECold%20weather%20can%20significantly%20impact%20an%20EV's%20range%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20put%20a%20damper%20on%20the%20whole%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20silver%202023%20Toyota%20bZ4X%20AWD%20Limited%20parked%20at%20a%20charging%20station%20in%20a%20parking%20lot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642c37d2fcb86b0018031149%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202023%20Toyota%20bZ4X%20AWD%20Limited%20charging.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20DC%20on%20a%20brisk%20April%20morning%20at%20about%205%20a.m.%20When%20I%20cranked%20up%20the%20heat%2C%20the%20BZ4X's%20estimated%20range%20dropped%20from%20176%20miles%20to%20an%20unsettling%20125%20miles.%20Keeping%20the%20cabin%20nice%20and%20toasty%20would%20have%20meant%20an%20extra%20charging%20stop%20and%20even%20more%20travel%20time%2C%20so%20instead%20I%20bundled%20up%20and%20shivered%20my%20way%20to%20sunrise.%20It%20wasn't%20much%20fun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECold%20temperatures%20deal%20a%20blow%20to%20EV%20range%20mainly%20because%20running%20the%20heater%20consumes%20lots%20of%20energy%20%E2%80%94%20energy%20that%20then%20can't%20be%20used%20for%20forward%20motion.%20In%20a%20gas%20car%2C%20the%20engine%20gives%20off%20heat%20as%20a%20byproduct.%20Consumer%20Reports%20ran%20tests%20on%20several%20EV%20models%20and%20found%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumerreports.org%2Fcars%2Fhybrids-evs%2Fhow-temperature-affects-electric-vehicle-range-a4873569949%2F%5C%22%3Ecold%20diminishes%20a%20car's%20range%20by%20around%2025%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cape%20Cod%20trip%20was%20in%20July%2C%20so%20I%20used%20the%20air%20conditioner%20a%20bit.%20That%20didn't%20draw%20much%20power%20at%20all%2C%20but%20did%20knock%20the%20range%20displayed%20in%20the%20Genesis's%20screen%20by%20a%20few%20miles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20Genesis%20GV60%20SUV%20charges%20at%20an%20EVgo%20charging%20station%2C%20with%20an%20overcast%20sky%20seen%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd3f6020f1cf0019cadd02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Genesis%20GV60%20charging.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20write%20off%20slow%20charging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20all%20about%20fast%20charging.%20I%20learned%20charging%20slowly%20while%20you're%20parked%20can%20make%20EV%20road%20trips%20more%20seamless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20arrived%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%20with%20a%206%25%20charge%20remaining%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20charge%20up%20before%20hitting%20the%20road%20back%20to%20New%20York.%20Although%20slow%20(also%20known%20as%20Level%202)%20charging%20plugs%20are%20becoming%20more%20common%20in%20apartment%20complexes%2C%20the%20one%20I%20visited%20in%20DC%20didn't%20have%20one.%20So%20I%20drove%20the%20BZ4X%20to%20a%20fast-charging%20station%20the%20following%20morning%20and%20left%20the%20car%20plugged%20in%20for%20an%20hour%20while%20sightseeing.%20It%20wasn't%20the%20worst%20inconvenience%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20vacations%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20about%20enjoying%20yourself%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20logistics%20of%20keeping%20your%20car%20from%20dying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Cape%20Cod%2C%20I%20stayed%20with%20friends%20who%20had%20a%20garage%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20a%20power%20outlet%20in%20that%20garage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Genesis%20GV60.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c41d66cf0778001966db19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Genesis%20GV60%20on%20a%20garage%20trickle%20charger.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenesis-gv60-ev-tesla-rival-facial-recognition-fingerprint-review-2023-7%5C%22%3Ethe%20GV60%3C%2Fa%3E%20plugged%20in%20for%20hours%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20weekend%20it%20recharged%20from%2020%25%20to%2065%25.%20Regular%20household%20outlets%20only%20provide%20a%20trickle%20of%20electricity%2C%20so%20EV%20owners%20can't%20rely%20on%20them%20exclusively.%20Still%2C%20the%20low-voltage%20plug%20gave%20the%20SUV%20enough%20juice%20to%20eliminate%20a%20charging%20detour%20and%20hit%20the%20road%20home%20with%20a%20solid%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20drivers%20never%20had%20to%20think%20all%20that%20hard%20about%20how%20their%20choice%20of%20vehicle%2C%20ambient%20temperature%2C%20or%20access%20to%20electrical%20plugs%20might%20affect%20a%20vacation.%20But%20it's%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20out%20there.%20And%20the%20best%20way%20to%20learn%20the%20ropes%20is%20to%20try%20things%20out%20for%20yourself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20love%20or%20hate%20your%20Tesla%20or%20other%20EV%3F%20Never%20buying%20to%20an%20electric%20car%20in%20a%20million%20years%3F%20I%20want%20to%20hear%20your%20thoughts%20about%20EVs.%20Contact%20me%20at%20tlevin%40insider.com%20and%20share%20your%20story!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-car-ev-road-trip-toyota-bz4x-genesis-gv60-charging-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691398801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd3d378