20Mr%20Johnson%20performed%20pool%20testing%20strips%20to%20discover%20his%20coffee%20pot%20had%20high%20levels%20of%20chlorine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Johnson%20pretended%20to%20continue%20drinking%20the%20coffee%20so%20he%20could%20wait%20until%20they%20returned%20to%20Davis%20Monthan%20Air%20Force%20Base%20before%20filing%20a%20police%20report%2C%20the%20media%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Johnson%20told%20investigators%20that%20he%20set%20up%20multiple%20hidden%20cameras%20again%20to%20catch%20her%20in%20the%20act.%20The%20footage%20showed%20Mrs%20Johnson%20%26quot%3Btake%20bleach%2C%20pour%20it%20into%20a%20container%20and%20then%20walk%20over%20and%20pour%20it%20into%20the%20coffee%20maker%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20indictment%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20was%20launched%20after%20Mr%20Johnson%20turned%20the%20footage%20over%20to%20police.%20Mr%20Johnson%20told%20police%20that%20his%20wife%20wanted%20to%20kill%20him%20to%20collect%20his%20death%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20is%20held%20in%20the%20Pima%20County%20Jail%20on%20%24250%2C000%20bond%20after%20prosecutors%20convinced%20a%20judge%20that%20she%20poses%20a%20flight%20risk%2C%20having%20recently%20purchased%20a%20house%20in%20the%20Philippines%20near%20the%20family%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fcrime%2Fhusband-murder-poison-melody-roby-johnson-b2388471.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMelody%20Johnson%20entered%20a%20not-guilty%20plea%20at%20an%20arraignment%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20next%20court%20appearance%20is%20scheduled%20for%206%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691398740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fmfgucgc_melody-felicano-johnson-_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-arrested-after-she-attempted-to-kill-husband