nt%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20on%20August%205%20that%20even%20two%20months%20after%20the%20new%20building%20was%20inaugurated%20%E2%80%93%20on%20May%2028%20%E2%80%93%20parliament%20is%20still%20functioning%20in%20the%20old%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20it%20evident%20that%20the%20building%20was%20formally%20inaugurated%20even%20when%20the%20construction%20was%20not%20finished%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20hasty%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20building%20in%20an%20undemocratic%20manner%20amounts%20to%20a%20deception%20of%20the%20people%20and%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20exposed.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20convey%20the%20strongest%20feeling%20of%20deception%20that%20we%20have%20experienced%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20MP%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESivadasan%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20current%20session%20of%20parliament%20has%20been%20underway%20for%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%20in%20the%20old%20building.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20haste%20which%20was%20shown%20in%20the%20inauguration%20has%20not%20been%20extended%20to%20the%20shifting%20of%20the%20actual%20functioning%20of%20the%20Parliament.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI(M)%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20inauguration%20did%20not%20follow%20several%20parliamentary%20traditions%2C%20like%20holding%20all-party%20meetings%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpresident-exclusion-parliament-inauguration-affront-constitution-people%5C%22%3Einviting%20the%20president%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20the%20head%20of%20the%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20haste%20was%20only%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20date%20of%20the%20inauguration%20coincided%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbirth%20anniversary%20of%20a%20person%20who%20had%20been%20charged%20as%20a%20co-conspirator%20in%20the%20assassination%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691395231000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16103200%2FGlimpses_of_t