rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.abplive.com%2Fnews%2Fi-am-fakir-what-can-my-rivals-do-to-me-pm-modi-in-moradabad-456949%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efakir%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Raj%20without%20batting%20an%20eyelid.%20That%20one%20person%20was%20never%20named%20the%20entire%20evening%2C%20though%20the%20actor%20brought%20him%20up%20again%20at%20the%20end%20when%20he%20said%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20should%20let%20one%20man%20be%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Evishwaguru%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20%5Bworld%20leader%5D%20but%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20should%20strive%20to%20become%20%3Cem%3Evishwamanavas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%2C%E2%80%9D%20using%20the%20word%20the%20great%20Kannada%20poet%20Kuvempu%20introduced%20to%20denote%20a%20citizen%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%20was%20speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20editor%20Seema%20Chishti%20at%20a%20ticketed%20event%20at%20the%20St%20John%E2%80%99s%20Medical%20College%20Auditorium%20as%20part%20of%20the%20news%20website%E2%80%99s%20public%20outreach%20and%20fund-raising%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20evening%20also%20featured%20the%20singer-educator%20Shabnam%20Virmani%20explaining%20and%20performing%20works%20from%20Kabir%20%E2%80%93%20the%20medieval%20Indian%20poet-saint%20whose%20work%20was%20deeply%20imbued%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20questions%20from%20Chishti%20and%20the%20audience%2C%20Prakash%20Raj%20spoke%20about%20the%20meaning%20of%20fraternity%2C%20why%20it%20was%20under%20strain%20in%20India%20today%2C%20the%20all-pervading%20sense%20of%20fear%20that%20seems%20to%20have%20gripped%20so%20many%20and%20the%20effect%20of%20this%20fear%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20film%20industry.%20he%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20work%20he%20is%20doing%2C%20especially%20through%20the%20medium%20of%20theatre%20to%20strengthen%20fraternity%2C%20and%20how%20he%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20fearlessness%20and%20broad-mindedness%20of%20the%20young%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20theme%20of%20the%20evening%2C%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%2C%20a%20founding%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98fraternity%E2%80%99%20figures%20prominently%20in%20the%20preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20alongside%20justice%2C%20liberty%20and%20equality%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20it%20is%20a%20word%20we%20often%20forget%20or%20ignore%20even%20though%20its%20spirit%20is%20so%20central%20to%20who%20we%20are%20as%20a%20people.%20Fraternity%20is%20that%20magical%20element%20that%20assures%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20us%20of%20our%20dignity%20as%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20and%2C%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20ensures%20our%20unity%20as%20a%20people%20and%20nation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20quoted%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20words%20to%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20in%201949%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CFraternity%20means%20a%20sense%20of%20common%20brotherhood%20of%20all%20Indians-of%20Indians%20being%20one%20people.%20It%20is%20the%20principle%20which%20gives%20unity%20and%20solidarity%20to%20social%20life%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20and%20said%20what%20this%20means%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Cif%20you%20attack%20the%20dignity%20of%20an%20individual%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20their%20ethnicity%20or%20language%2C%20religion%20or%20caste%2C%20sexuality%20or%20food%20habits%20or%20beliefs%20%E2%80%93%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ethen%20you%20attack%20the%20very%20foundations%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07111456%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-07-at-11.00.11-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C