d%20announced%20a%20social%20and%20economic%20boycott%20of%20Muslims.%20This%20was%20the%20area%20where%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgurugram-mosque-set-on-fire-was-the-only-one-of-govt-allocated-land-in-the-area%5C%22%3Emosque%20was%20attacked%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20deputy%20imam%20murdered%20by%20a%20Hindutva%20mob%20during%20communal%20violence%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20held%20in%20Tigra%20village%2C%20which%20is%20close%20to%20the%20Anjuman%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20attending%20the%20meeting%20also%20alleged%20that%20people%20who%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20attacking%20the%20mosque%20are%20%E2%80%9Cinnocent%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fgurugram-news%2Fvillagers-in-gurugram-gather-call-for-boycott-of-muslims-after-mosque-attack-demand-release-of-arrested-suspects-101691345115330.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20and%20demanded%20that%20there%20names%20be%20dropped%20from%20the%20case%20within%20seven%20days.%20Otherwise%20they%20have%20threatened%20a%20%3Cem%3Echakka-jam%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESube%20Singh%20Bohra%2C%20former%20sarpanch%20of%20Wazirabad%20in%20Sector%2057%2C%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20see%20the%20evidence%20against%20the%20men%20that%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20violence.%20The%20families%20are%20being%20harassed%20and%20targeted%20by%20those%20living%20near%20the%20mosque%2C%20but%20we%20will%20not%20let%20this%20happen%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20hundreds%20of%20Muslim%20men%20working%20in%20Gurugram%20as%20carpenters%2C%20barbers%2C%20vegetable%20vendors%2C%20mechanics%2C%20and%20cab%20drivers%2C%20and%20we%20have%20always%20supported%20them%2C%20but%20now%20we%20will%20ensure%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20any%20support%20from%20anywhere%20as%20they%20are%20responsible%20for%20disrupting%20peace%20in%20the%20city.%20Muslims%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20love%20or%20work%20in%20the%20city.%20We%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20city%20not%20to%20rent%20out%20apartments%20or%20slums%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kulbhushan%20Bhardwaj%2C%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20member%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDLF%20Gurugram%20senior%20police%20officer%20Vikas%20Kaushik%20told%20ANI%20that%20the%20organisers%20had%20told%20the%20police%20the%20event%20would%20be%20peaceful.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20past%20two-three%20days%2C%20Gurugram%20has%20been%20peaceful.%20No%20incident%20has%20been%20reported.%20We%20feel%20that%20today%E2%80%99s%20panchayat%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20peacefully.%20We%20have%20had%20talks%20with%20all%20sides.%20They%20have%20assured%20us%20that%20the%20panchayat%20will%20happen%20peacefully%E2%80%A6%20The%20panchayat%20starts%20at%209%20am.%20Some%20500-1%2C000%20people%20are%20expected%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kaushik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20did%20not%20say%20why%20police%20was%20not%20intervening%20despite%20prohibitory%20orders%20being%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20flagged%20this%20boycott%20call%20on%20Sunday%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20letter%20that%20made%20the%20same%20demand%20written%20by%20a%20panchayat%20sarpanch%20on%20his%20official%20letterhead.%20A%20four-member%20delegation%20from%20the%20party%20also%20visited%20affected%20areas%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20letter%20on%20the%20letterhead%20of%20the%20Jainabad%20Panchayat%20Sarpanch%20Bhavna%20Yadav%2C%20from%20Block%20Dahina%2C%20District%20Rewari%2C%20Haryana%2C%20exposes%20the%20bitter%20reality%20of%20organised%20discrimination%20against%20minorities%20which%20is%20being%20bred%20systematically%20under%20the%20BJP%20rule%2C%E2%80%9D%20CPI%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fcommunal-violence-communist-party-of-india-delegation-in-haryana-flags-muslim-boycott-call%2Fcid%2F1957186%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20content%20of%20the%20letter%20is%20shocking.%20It%20submits%20to%20the%20local%20police%20authorities%20a%20decision%20to%20not%20allow%20Muslims%20or%20miscreants%20to%20do%20any%20business%20or%20hawker%20activity%20in%20the%20panchayat%20area.%20It%20also%20equalises%20Muslims%20to%20burglars%20and%20cattle-thieves%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20letter%20says%20that%20these%20steps%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20ensure%20peace%20in%20the%20village%2C%20automatically%20making%20Muslim%20presence%20the%20sole%20reason%20for%20communal%20disturbance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691382654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105433%2F4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindu-mahapanchayat-held-without-permission-in-gurugram-calls-for-boycott-of-muslims%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Those%20attending%20the%20meeting%20also%20alleged%20that%20people%20who%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20attacking%20the%20mosque%20in%20Gurugram%20are%20%26quot%3Binnocent%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindu-mahapanchayat-held-without-permission-in-gurugram-calls-for-boycott-of-muslims%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Love%20in%20Taipei%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Romance%20and%20Self-Discovery%20Take%20a%20Holiday%20In%20a%20Flat%20Coming-of-Age%20Film%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691380800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FLOVE_IN_TAIPEI_D5_2L5A0909_RT.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2