20two%20KPA%20MLAs%20currently%20in%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20are%20Kimneo%20Hangshing%20and%20Chinlunthang%2C%20representing%20the%20Saikul%20and%20Singat%20constituencies%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20KPA%20is%20a%20new%20party%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20formed%20in%202022%20and%20contested%20its%20first%20elections%20in%20the%20same%20year.%20Members%20of%20the%20party%20had%20attended%20the%20NDA%20meet%20held%20in%20Delhi%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20eight%20other%20Kuki%20MLAs%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20all%20from%20the%20BJP.%20While%20they%20have%20openly%20criticised%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20conflict%2C%20they%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20government.%20All%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-kuki-zomi-mlas-separate-administration%5C%22%3Eearlier%20urged%20the%20Union%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20separate%20administration%20under%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20and%20let%20people%20from%20their%20community%20%E2%80%9Clive%20peacefully%20as%20neighbours%20with%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20assembly%20is%20supposed%20to%20convene%20on%20August%2021.%20The%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Churachandpur%2C%20L.M.%20Khaute%2C%20has%20already%20said%20he%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20attend%20the%20session%20%E2%80%9Cin%20view%20of%20the%20prevailing%20law%20and%20order%20situation%E2%80%9D%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20three%20months%20have%20passed%20since%20ethnic%20conflict%20erupted%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%20and%20the%20violence%20is%20showing%20no%20signs%20of%20abating.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20six%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20fresh%20rounds%20of%20violence%20%E2%80%93%20leading%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2Fmore-centr