rns%E2%80%9D%20about%20its%20cricket%20team%E2%80%99s%20security%2C%20the%20foreign%20office%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20conveying%20these%20concerns%20to%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20and%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%20We%20expect%20that%20full%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Team%20will%20be%20ensured%20during%20its%20visit%20to%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20further%20claimed%20that%20Pakistan%20believes%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstate%20of%20bilateral%20relations%20with%20India%20should%20not%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20fulfilling%20its%20international%20sports-related%20obligations%E2%80%9D.%20It%20also%20contrasted%20Pakistan%20as%20having%20shown%20a%20%E2%80%9Cconstructive%20and%20responsible%20approach%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20India%E2%80%99s%20intransigent%20attitude%2C%20as%20the%20latter%20had%20refused%20to%20send%20its%20Cricket%20Team%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20largely%20been%20hostile%20for%20the%20last%20six%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20diplomatic%20ties%20were%20officially%20downgraded%20in%202019%20when%20the%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20dissolution%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Najam%20Sethi-led%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20had%20come%20to%20an%20understanding%20that%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20would%20be%20held%20under%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1752482%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20meant%20that%20the%20matches%20will%20be%20divided%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20another%20neutral%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20effectively%20allow%20India%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20even%20though%20BCCI%20was%20adamant%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%20will%20not%20travel%