n%20a%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20realise%20how%20much%20harm%20we%20do%20to%20the%20environment%20with%20our%20daily%20activities.%20We%20might%20think%20that%20these%20glass%20bottles%20go%20to%20recycling%20but%20the%20ground%20reality%20is%20quite%20different.%20Most%20of%20them%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhuri%20met%20Amit%20while%20working%20in%20the%20media%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CAmit%20and%20I%20had%20a%20very%20similar%20outlook%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326200%2Fecosoul-home-india-boston-sustainable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elife%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fa%3E%20We%20would%20chat%20about%20how%20we%20could%20do%20something%20about%20it%20and%20ended%20up%20brainstorming%20ideas%20for%20hours.%20Being%20in%20the%20media%20industry%2C%20both%20of%20us%20were%20exposed%20first-hand%20to%20innovators%20around%20the%20world%20who%20were%20working%20in%20the%20sustainability%20field.%20We%20often%20heard%20topics%20like%20solar%20energy%2C%20upcycling%2C%20reusing%2C%20and%20recycling%20around%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLooking%20at%20so%20many%20people%20working%20towards%20sustainability%2C%20we%20thought%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Hum%20bhi%20kar%20sakte%20hai%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(we%20can%20do%20it%20too).%20So%20in%202013%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%2C%E2%80%9D%20Madhuri%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20sustainability%20and%20carbon%20footprint%20was%20not%20as%20popular%20as%20today.%20People%20were%20not%20as%20well-informed%20about%20the%20harm%20we%20do%20to%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20many%20did%20not%20care%20about%20what%20happened%20to%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-capti