3Cp%3EThis%20gave%20Madhuri%20and%20Amit%20the%20push%20that%20they%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUpcycling%20bottles%20into%20functional%20art%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20decided%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20dedicate%20themselves%20to%20their%20venture.%20They%20started%20%E2%80%98Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%E2%80%99%20in%202013%2C%20and%20have%20converted%20over%20seven%20lakh%20glass%20bottles%20into%20pieces%20of%20home%20utility%20and%20decor%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20had%20sustainability%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20project%2C%20we%20also%20wanted%20to%20earn%20money%20so%20we%20could%20pay%20off%20the%20rag%20pickers%20and%20other%20employees.%20So%20we%20started%20to%20host%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274565%2Flibrarian-grows-vegetable-fruits-flowers-on-terrace-gardening-facebook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarious%20Facebook%20campaigns%3C%2Fa%3E%20urging%20people%20to%20come%20join%20us%20with%20their%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20advertised%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20caught%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20%E2%80%94%20we%20asked%20them%20to%20come%20with%20their%20bottles%20and%20that%20we%20would%20convert%20the%20bottles%20into%20whatever%20piece%20they%20fancied.%20This%20gave%20a%20boost%20to%20our%20business%2C%20and%20by%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%20we%20started%20getting%20flooded%20with%20orders%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20products%20are%20priced%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%20300%20and%20Rs%201%2C600.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20did%20not%20have%20any%20formal%20training%20in%20working%20with%20glass%2C%20so%20they%20had%20their%20fair%20share%20of%20mistakes.%20%E2%80%9CGlass%20breaks%20very%20easily%20and%20we%20have%20to%20be%20quite%20careful%20with%20it.%20We%20used%20the%20internet%20and%20hired%20some%20glass%20artists%20to%20help%20us%20with%20the%20process.%20We%20have%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20hits%20and%20misses%2C%20but%20it%20is%20practice%20alone%20that%20has%20helped%20us%20come%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Madhuri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Madhuri%20collects%20bottles%20from%20customers%20and%20ragpickers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326398%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThey%20collect%20glass%20bottles%20and%20convert%20them%20into%20serving%20sets%2C%20platters%2C%20lamps%20etc%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Madhuri%20Balodi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20they%20focus%20on%20the%20finishing%20touches%20very%20carefully%20so%20the%20products%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20upcycled%2C%20but%20rather%20feel%20brand%20new!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20social%20media%20campaigns%20also%20resulted%20in%20something%20very%20sweet%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20came%20to%20us%20with%20their%20bottles%2C%20many%20shared%20special%20stories%20behind%20each%20of%20them!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20people%20saying%20things%20like%20%E2%80%98I%20opened%20this%20bottle%20when%20my%20daughter%20was%20born%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98My%20best%20friend%20gifted%20me%20this%20bottle%2020%20years%20ago%E2%80%99.%20They%20come%20to%20us%20with%20requests%20to%20save%20the%20bottles%20and%20preserve%20them%20in%20a%20memorable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhuri%20and%20Amit%20share%20that%20such%20requests%20and%20stories%20make%20their%20jobs%20even%20more%20special%20and%20add%20an%20element%20of%20challenge%20to%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20journey%20from%20waste%20to%20wonder%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20the%20process%20of%20upcycling%20starts%2C%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20ways%20in%20which%20we%20collect%20bottles.%20First%2C%20through%20our%20BYOB%20(bring%20your%20own%20bottle)%20initiative%2C%20we%20transform%20the%20bottles%20that%20people%20bring%20to%20us%20into%20whatever%20they%20request%20them%20to%20be.%20Second%2C%20we%20collaborate%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300446%2Ffriends-help-ragpickers-in-kolkata-slum-launch-sustainable-children-fashion-brand-khudey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20with%20rag%20pickers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20collect%20and%20bring%20bottles%20to%20us%2C%20for%20which%20we%20pay%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20and%20Madhuri%20have%20a%20network%20of%20more%20than%20150%20ragpickers%20in%20and%20around%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20collected%20bottles%20are%20sanitised%2C%20and%20then%20a%20rough%20design%20is%20made.%20We%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%20into%20what%20can%20be%20made%20out%20of%20these%20bottles.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20people%20to%20just%20view%20them%20as%20pieces%20of%20decor.%20We%20want%20to%20promote%20the%20reuse%20of%20products%2C%20so%20we%20make%20utility%20items%20like%20platters%20and%20bowls%20out%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Madhuri%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20firmly%20believes%20that%20upcycling%20is%20the%20way%20forward%20and%20wants%20more%20businesses%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuzrPPOhBpG%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuzrPPOhBpG%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuzrPPOhBpG%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%20(%40kavipoetryart)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pandemic%20significantly%20boosted%20the%20sustainability%20movement.%20Previously%2C%20people%20viewed%20products%20as%20mere%20consumables%20and%20were%20hesitant%20to%20invest%20in%20them.%20However%2C%20the%20situation%20has%20completely%20transformed.%20People%20are%20now%20eager%20to%20make%20extra%20efforts%20to%20avoid%20contributing%20to%20global%20warming%20and%20carbon%20emissions.%20This%20presents%20an%20opportune%20moment%20for%20new%20businesses%20to%20emerge%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20been%20in%20this%20business%20for%20almost%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20duo%20now%20have%20customers%20from%20all%20across%20the%20country%20and%20abroad.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20strong%20customer%20base%20of%20over%2080%2C000%20people%20from%20India%20as%20well%20as%20Canada%2C%20Netherlands%2C%20Dubai%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20our%20project%2C%20we%20want%20to%20give%20people%20an%20alternative%20and%20an%20opportunity%20to%20live%20sustainably.%20This%20project%20is%20beyond%20just%20business%20for%20us%20as%20this%20is%20for%20the%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Madhuri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20send%20them%20your%20glass%20bottles%2C%20contact%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkavipoetryart%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691155506000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326377%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Noida-based%20Madhuri%20Balodi%20and%20Amit%20Singh%20started%20%E2%80%98Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%E2%80%99%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20creative%20way%20of%20saving%20glass%20bottles%20from%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills.%20They%20collect%20bottles%20from%20ragpickers%20and%20customers%20and%20transform%20them%20into%20functional%20art%20items.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326377%2Fnoida-madhuri-balodi-amit-singh-kavi-the-poetry-art-project-glass-bottle-art-sustainability-home-decor%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20to%20Expect%20at%20COP28%20UAE%3A%20A%20Global%20Movement%20to%20Fight%20Climate%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EClimate%20action%20requires%20the%20collaboration%20and%20cooperation%20of%20individuals%2C%20communities%2C%20organisations%2C%20and%20governments.%20And%20to%20mitigate%20its%20effects%2C%20we%20need%20to%20shift%20from%20incremental%20steps%20to%20transformational%20progress%20that%20delivers%20for%20everyone%2C%20everywhere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20exactly%20what%20COP28%20will%20seek%20to%20achieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20COP%20and%20why%20is%20it%20important%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20is%20the%20supreme%20decision-making%20body%20for%20all%20States%20that%20are%20Parties%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Framework%20Convention%20on%20Climate%20Change%20(UNFCCC).%20The%20UNFCCC%20came%20into%20force%20on%2021%20March%201994%20with%20the%20aim%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20prevent%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous%E2%80%9D%20human%20interference%20with%20the%20climate%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20COP%20meets%20every%20year%20to%20assess%20the%20progress%20that%20has%20been%20made%20towards%20this.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20meetings%20have%20resulted%20in%20several%20legally%20binding%20international%20agreements%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20including%20the%202015%20Paris%20Agreement%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%20well%20below%202%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20pre-industrial%20levels%20and%20pursue%20efforts%20to%20limit%20the%20temperature%20increase%20to%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECOP28%20UAE%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028th%20COP%20is%20being%20hosted%20by%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20at%20Expo%20City%20Dubai%20between%2030%20November%20and%2012%20December%202023.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20COP%20of%20unity%2C%20solidarity%2C%20and%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECOP28%20will%20see%20the%20first%20Global%20Stocktake%20(GST)%2C%20a%20process%20mandated%20by%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20to%20evaluate%20advancements%20towards%20its%20objectives.%20It%20is%20against%20this%20backdrop%20that%20COP28%20will%20bring%20everyone%20to%20the%20table%20to%20recalibrate%2C%20raise%20ambitions%20and%20maximise%20the%20opportunities%20of%20the%20clean%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20of%20this%20year%2C%20the%20UAE%20hosted%20the%20annual%20Abu%20Dhabi%20Sustainability%20Week%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286865%2Feasy-steps-to-be-sustainable-at-home-no-plastic-use-save-money-sustainability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%20event%20established%20in%202008%20to%20accelerate%20sustainable%20economic%20development%20and%20facilitate%20partnerships%20to%20enable%20the%20energy%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20XX%20edition%20of%20ADSW%20drove%20momentum%20between%20COP27%20and%20COP28%2C%20enabling%20impactful%20and%20continuous%20dialogue%20between%20key%20stakeholders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20was%20the%20first%20country%20in%20the%20region%20to%20announce%20its%20commitment%20to%20Net%20Zero%20and%20has%20a%20proud%20track%20record%20of%20investing%20in%20the%20energy%20transition.%20This%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271708%2Fstartup-innovation-convert-renewable-energy-water-uravu-labs-bengaluru-engineer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewable%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E%20powerhouse%2C%20Masdar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20Climate%20Leadership%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMasdar%20was%20established%20in%202006%20as%20part%20of%20the%20UAE%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20vision%20to%20diversify%20its%20economy%20and%20bring%20about%20a%20cycle%20of%20growth%20and%20innovation.%20His%20Excellency%20Dr%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%2C%20the%20COP%20President%20Designate%2C%20is%20Masdar%E2%80%99s%20founding%20CEO%20and%20current%20Chairman.%20Under%20his%20leadership%2C%20the%20company%20has%20grown%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20investors%20in%20renewable%20energy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Masdar%20has%20a%20combined%20investment%20portfolio%20valued%20at%20%2430bn.%20It%20is%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20climate%20innovation%2C%20operating%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F287058%2Frenewable-energy-map-india-wind-power-plants-project-largest-solar-park-environment-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting-edge%20renewable%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20improving%20lives%20in%20over%2040%20countries%20across%206%20continents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EH.E.%20Dr%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%20brings%20over%2020%20years%20of%20industry%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20to%20the%20role%20of%20COP%20President-Designate%20and%20is%20uniquely%20positioned%20to%20drive%20critical%20negotiations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20of%20the%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20preeminent%20climate%20champions%2C%20Dr%20Sultan%20has%20outlined%20his%20plans%20to%20deliver%20a%20COP%20for%20all%2C%20underpinned%20by%20the%20belief%20that%20everyone%20must%20be%20on%20board%20in%20order%20to%20accelerate%20progress.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2013%20days%2080%2C000%20participants%2C%20including%20140%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20government%20will%20meet%20in%20the%20UAE%20to%20reduce%20emissions%2C%20protect%20biodiversity%2C%20and%20support%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288116%2Fwhat-antarcticas-40c-weather-iceberg-graveyard-taught-me-about-climate-change%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffected%20by%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20moving%20fast%20enough%2C%20but%20we%20also%20know%20that%20we%20have%20the%20power%20to%20achieve%20a%20more%20sustainable%20and%20prosperous%20future%2C%20if%20we%20act%20in%20solidarity.%20COP-28%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20uniting%20everyone%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20drafted%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Masdar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funfccc.int%2Fprocess%2Fbodies%2Fsupreme-bodies%2Fconference-of-the-parties-cop%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUnited%20Nations%20Cl%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funfccc.int%2Fprocess%2Fbodies%2Fsupreme-bodies%2Fconference-of-the-parties-cop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eimate%20Change%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalmediainsight.com%2Fblog%2Fcop28-global-climate-summit-uae%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOP%2028%20UAE%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20UN%20Climate%20Change%20Conference%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20Global%20Media%20Insight%2C%20Published%20on%2023%20June%202023%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3