0for%20eco-friendly%20alternatives.%20This%20realisation%20became%20our%20%3Cem%3Eaha%3C%2Fem%3E%20moment!%20We%20recognised%20that%20the%20market%20was%20ripe%20for%20disruption%20and%20that%20sustainable%20products%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20gain%20significant%20traction%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arvind%2C%20co-founder%2C%20EcoSoul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20wave%20of%20transformation%20in%20consumer%20behaviour%20towards%20sustainability%20came%20in%20the%20food%20category.%20Today%2C%20many%20are%20consuming%20organic%2C%20unprocessed%20food.%20So%2C%20we%20figured%20the%20next%20breakout%20category%20had%20to%20be%20something%20that%20touches%20the%20food.%20For%20instance%2C%20your%20tabletop%20line%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20decided%20to%20sell.%20We%20wanted%20to%20disrupt%20this%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2040-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founders%20quit%20their%20jobs%20in%20June%202020%2C%20right%20when%20COVID%20was%20beginning%20to%20rear%20its%20head%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20basically%20solving%20for%20the%20three%20big%20As%20%E2%80%94%20awareness%2C%20affordability%20and%20availability.%20Awareness%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20big%20problem%20as%20most%20people%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20harm%20that%20plastic%20causes.%20We%20had%20to%20keep%20our%20prices%20within%2025%20percent%20of%20single-use%20plastic%20to%20make%20it%20affordable.%20The%20major%20challenge%20was%20availability%20as%20we%20started%20during%20COVID%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20make%20their%20products%20widely%20available%2C%20they%20had%20to%20work%20on%20a%20strong%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20this%20would%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315625%2Fdelhi-meeta-sharma-gupta-shumee-sustainable-toy-brand-develop-cognitive-motor-skills-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_