98Anything%20that%20can%20go%20wrong%20will%20go%20wrong%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20when%20they%20worked%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20building%20a%20supply%20chain%20amidst%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20faced%20multiple%20challenges%20from%20raw%20material%20shortages%20to%20transportation%20bottlenecks%2C%20sky-high%20container%20prices%20and%20labour%20force%20constraints.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CFinding%20big%20players%20in%20India%20in%20this%20segment%20was%20difficult.%20In%20China%2C%20a%20sugarcane%20bagasse%20factory%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%20150-200%20tonnes%20per%20day%2C%20while%20in%20India%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20two%20tonnes.%20The%20scale%20difference%20is%20huge.%20We%20had%20to%20work%20on%20scaling%20up%2C%20which%20we%20did.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20built%20a%20large%20factory%20for%20producing%20palm%20leaf%20plates%20in%20Tumakuru%2C%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20small%20cottage%20industries%20in%20the%20palm%20leaf%20segment.%20So%20we%20worked%20with%20the%20Krishikalpa%20Foundation%20to%20build%20a%20large%20factory.%20Farmers%20from%2021%20districts%20came%20together%20and%20built%20a%20factory%20which%20has%2045%20machines%20today.%20All%20the%20products%20are%20exported%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202021%2C%20they%20started%20selling%20six%20products%2C%20including%20palm%20leaf%20plates%20and%20bamboo-based%20cutlery%20online%20in%20North%20America.%20They%20replaced%20plastic%20in%20everyday%20products%2C%20such%20as%20forks%2C%20spoons%2C%20cups%2C%20straws%2C%20plates%20etc.%20They%20also%20replaced%20paper%20with%20their%20compostable%20paper%20towels%2C%20which%20are%20actually%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20agro-waste%20to%20make%20our%20products.%20We%20work%20with%20sugarcane%20bagasse%2C%20rice%20khus%2C%20wheat%20khus%2C%20and%20palm%20leaves.%20We%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20cut%20any%20trees%20to%20make%20our%20products.%20All%20our%20finished%20products%20are%20replacements%20for%20single-use%20plastics%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rahul%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20their%20products%20are%20%E2%80%9Cearthworm%20certified.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20plastic%20or%20cut%20trees%2C%20all%20our%20products%20are%20compostable.%20It%E2%80%99s%20good%20for%20soil%20health.%20Even%20earthworms%20can%20eat%20it%20after%20it%20gets%20composted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ecosoul%20cutlery%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-1536x1536.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326248%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEco-friendly%20cutlery%20by%20EcoSoul%20Home.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20aim%20to%20provide%20consumers%20with%20