0a%20variety%20of%20jaggery%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20full%20of%20nutrients%20that%20helps%20in%20fighting%20disease%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECome%20winter%20and%20out%20come%20the%20jars%20of%20jaggery%2C%20a%20common%20sight%20on%20the%20chequered%20dining%20tables%20of%20Indian%20homes.%20But%20all%20varieties%20of%20jaggery%20pale%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Enolen%20gur%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20healthiest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20its%20origins%20date%20to%20as%20early%20as%204th%20century%20BC%2C%20when%20artisans%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Siulis%E2%80%99%20residing%20in%20Pundra%20Bardhan%20(now%20Bogra)%20in%20Bengal%20would%20extract%20the%20sap%20of%20the%20date%20palm%20tree%20to%20sell%20in%20markets.%20The%20extraction%20was%20no%20easy%20process%20and%20would%20involve%20a%20gritty%20feat%20of%20scaling%20the%20thorny%20date%20palm%20trees%20at%20night%20to%20cut%20the%20flower%20cluster%20at%20the%20end.%20Timing%20was%20of%20the%20essence%20as%20the%20minute%20the%20climate%20would%20turn%20humid%2C%20wet%2C%20or%20even%20rainy%2C%20the%20sap%20would%20begin%20to%20turn%20turbid.%20With%20time%20the%20artisans%20got%20better%20at%20their%20task%20and%20%3Cem%3Enolen%20gur%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecame%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302410%2Fhistory-of-nolen-gur-jaggery-health-benefits-winter-food-bengali-desserts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estaple%20in%20Bengal%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20throughout%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Delhi%20%26amp%3B%20Chole%20Bhature%3A%20An%20unending%20love%20story%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCveKS5kNtTJ%2F%3Futm_sou