.%20By%202020%2C%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20Kirat%20had%20made%20up%20his%20mind%20to%20return%20home%20and%20start%20looking%20for%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20product%20that%20highlights%20our%20culture%20to%20the%20upcoming%20generations.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20open%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20for%20people%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20Bodo%20culture.%20What%20could%20be%20a%20better%20way%20of%20introducing%20kids%20and%20people%20to%20my%20culture%20than%20with%20soft%20toys%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20started%20Zankla%20Studio%20in%202021%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20showcasing%20the%20rich%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F135223%2Fassam-bodoland-lakme-women-weavers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20culture%20of%20the%20Bodo%20Tribe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20studio%20creates%20handmade%20plastic-free%20soft%20toys%20that%20narrate%20stories%20deeply%20connected%20to%20the%20local%20culture%20and%20traditions%20of%20the%20Bodo%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERepresenting%20people%20from%20the%20Bodo%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Each%20toy%20created%20at%20Zankla%20Studio%20carries%20a%20narrative%20native%20to%20the%20tribe%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetteri