5823%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUmer%20with%20his%20parents.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Umer%20Ahmad%20Ganie%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20reason%20why%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20labourer%20was%20so%20that%20I%20could%20afford%20my%20education.%20Due%20to%20the%20low-income%20situation%20at%20home%2C%20my%20family%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20support%20me%20further.%20I%20had%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20support%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmer%20started%20to%20work%20as%20a%20daily%20wage%20worker%2C%20mostly%20working%20as%20a%20painter.%20He%20earned%20Rs%20550%20a%20day%2C%20which%20he%20used%20to%20pay%20for%20his%20books%20and%20to%20bring%20food%20for%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20his%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%2C%20Umer%20remarks%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAb%20is%20gareebi%20se%20bahar%20nikalna%20hai.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(I%20want%20to%20break%20this%20cycle%20of%20poverty).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20are%20young%2C%20you%20dream%20of%20different%20things%20unaware%20of%20the%20circumstances%20life%20may%20throw%20at%20you.%20When%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20I%20dreamt%20of%20becoming%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321822%2Fraised-by-single-mom-ias-officer-donge-revaiah-shares-inspiring-upsc-journey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20an%20IAS%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20as%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20much%20money%20this%20would%20cost%20me.%20For%20starters%2C%20I%20will%20need%20a%20graduation%20degree!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20if%20you%20ask%20me%20now%20what%20I%20want%20to%20be%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20simply%20say%20I%20want%20to%20break%20this%20cycle%20of%20poverty.%20Generations%20in%20my%20f