%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20school%20and%20work%2C%20I%20would%20return%20at%207%20pm.%20Once%20home%2C%20I%20would%20not%20waste%20even%20a%20minute%20after%20that.%20I%20used%20to%20study%20till%20midnight%20and%20then%20get%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20of%20sleep%2C%20then%20wake%20up%20to%20study%20some%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20followed%20the%20routine%20very%20strictly%20because%20I%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20am%20not%20consistent%20then%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20crack%20the%20exam%20and%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20another%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20routine%20and%20his%20motivation%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20routine%20was%20very%20tiring%2C%20and%20I%20would%20not%20get%20enough%20rest%20sometimes.%20But%20I%20had%20to%20do%20it!%20I%20kept%20believing%20in%20myself%20and%20that%20my%20hard%20work%20would%20pay%20off.%20I%20kept%20picturing%20a%20time%20when%20my%20family%20and%20I%20would%20be%20out%20of%20poverty%E2%80%A6not%20worrying%20about%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Learn%2C%20revise%20and%20repeat%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20crack%20the%20NEET%20exam%2C%20most%20of%20the%20aspirants%20turn%20towards%20coaching%20and%20private%20assistance.%20But%20for%20Umer%2C%20that%20was%20not%20an%20option.%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20not%20take%20any%20coaching%20because%20of%20two%20reasons.%20One%2C%20I%20could%20not%20afford%20them%2C%20and%20two%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20spare%20the%20time%20to%20attend%20extra%20classes%20while%20I%20juggled%20school%20and%20labour.%20Instead%2C%20I%20used%20the%20internet%20and%20NCERT%20to%20crack%20the%20paper%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20resources%20online%2C%20he%20found%20some%20helpful%20lectures%20on%20YouTube.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20found%20a%20free%20lecture%20online%20by%20Physics%20Wallah%20and%20then%20d