lt%3D%5C%22Senthil%20informs%20that%20since%202019%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20catered%20to%20more%20than%20three%20lakh%20mothers%20from%2014%2C328%20villages%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Kerala.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325681%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESenthil%20informs%20that%20since%202019%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20catered%20to%20more%20than%2030%20lakh%20mothers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20concern%20for%20her%20drove%20him%20to%20develop%20a%20prototype%20of%20a%20device%20that%20could%20monitor%20one%E2%80%99s%20vitals%20like%20blood%20glucose%20and%20blood%20pressure.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20my%20sister%20does%20not%20go%20into%20the%20labour%20room%20with%20any%20complications%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20experience%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20women%20face%20significant%20challenges%20when%20visiting%20hospitals%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F72679%2Fcare-nx-doorstep-diagnosis-innovative-technology-pregnancy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantenatal%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20long%20travel%20times%20and%20waiting%20periods%20of%20five%20to%20six%20hours%20for%20a%20short%20consultation%20lead%20many%20women%20to%20avoid%20these%20