edia.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325679%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESenthil%20felt%20inspired%20to%20assist%20more%20women%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20rural%20and%20remote%20areas.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20give%20our%20medical%20device%20called%20AlloTricorder%20to%20healthcare%20workers.%20They%20use%20it%20to%20measure%20vital%20parameters%20like%20blood%20pressure%2C%20blood%20glucose%2C%20ECG%2C%20and%20temperature%20%E2%80%94%20all%20using%20a%20single%20device.%20They%20then%20digitally%20transfer%20the%20data%20via%20Bluetooth%20to%20the%20application%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20collected%20at%20hospitals%20is%20the%20same%20as%20what%20we%20capture%20at%20home.%20Our%20idea%20was%20to%20gather%20this%20data%20right%20at%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20home.%20If%20lab%20tests%20are%20necessary%2C%20we%20collect%20the%20samples%20from%20their%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20device%20is%20unique%20as%20other%20tools%20available%20in%20the%20market%20are%20mainly%20for%20foetal%20monitoring.%20However%2C%20we%20still%20recommend%20that%20women%20visit%20the%20hospital%20every%20month%2C%20where%20the%20doctor%20can%20review%20the%20monthly%20data%20and%20prescribe%20medication%20accordingly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he%2