dia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_20221130_091137_1_11zon-1690466114-150x67.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325419%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221147%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELisbon%20Ferrao%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Vasai%20Beach%20Cleaners%E2%80%99%20is%20an%20initiative%20to%20clean%20the%20plastic%20trash%20on%20Mumbai%20beaches%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Lisbon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELisbon%20Ferrao%20heads%20the%20group%20%E2%80%98Vasai%20Beach%20Cleaners%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20intent%20on%20giving%20Mumbaikars%20their%20spotless%20sands%20back.%20He%20was%20shocked%20when%20he%20saw%20his%20kids%20playing%20with%20plastic%20instead%20of%20sand%20due%20to%20the%20abundance%20of%20plastic%20waste%20on%20the%20beach.%20Motivated%20to%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20he%20formed%20a%20group%20of%20young%20environmentalists%20who%20now%20spend%20their%20weekends%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F258032%2Fudhampur-bowli-water-conservation-how-to-rejuvenate-natural-water-source-springs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaning%20up%20trash%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Mumbai%20beaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELisbon%20shares%20that%20they%20have%20cleared%20over%20650%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20to%20date.%20The%20collected%20garbage%20includes%20backpacks%2C%20cement%20bags%2C%20milk%20packets%2C%20fishing%20nets%2C%20ropes%2C%20single-use%20cups%2C%20bags%2C%20toys%2C%20toothbrushes%2C%20medicines%20bottles%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20extend%20the%20process%20of%20sustainability%2C%20the%20equipment%20for%20collecting%20the%20trash%20is%20reusable%20too.%20This%20includes%20cement%20bags%2C%20tarps%2C%20sheets%2C%20and%20safety%20gloves%20that%20are%20washed%20after%20each%20cleanup%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20collected%20plastic%20being%20burnt%20in%20landf